  "description" : "* Based on a comedy manga by http://anidb.net/cr84872 [Nyan Nyan Factory].\nWelcome to http://anidb.net/ch153362 [Yani]`s apartment. Please don`t mind the smell. Yani is a catgirl with a seriously bad smoking habit. Every time she tries to quit, she becomes weak to the cravings and gives in almost instantly. Behind on her rent and unable to hold down a job, her friends and sister rally around to help her out. But when she`s using her pee to put out cigarette fires, they may just have their work cut out for them.\nWill she ever get her life together, or is she doomed to live as a chainsmoking slob forever?\nSource: Seven Seas Entertainment",
